<Author>carloswill
<Content>Great value and location...a little noisy. Great value... a little noisy.I cant believe some of the other reviews. I paid $35 online and felt like I got a really good deal. The walk up rate was more than twice the online rate.The room was nicely decorated and exceptionally clean. There is rarely a need for heat... so the room was a little cool... but the staff brought me extra blankets the moment I requested them. Overall, the staff was professional, friendly, knowledgable and multi-lingual. The location cant be beat for a budget traveler... steps from the best subway lines in the city. 15 cents per trip. Lots of dining choices nearby and convenience stores and internet cafes.This hotel is ON Reforma Blvd... so it is safe at all hours... but it is also quite noisy at all hours, especially the lower level rooms.If you are a light sleeper, do your research and find something in a quieter area. 
