<Author>carefulraveler
<Content>Would stay there again! The staff was friendly and helpful. The room was clean and the beds were comfortable. The location was good, next to a metro station. There were good food and drink vendors close by.There were some times without hot water, but it was usually nice and hot in the mornings. The room was chilly but not unbearable. Out leaky toilet was repaired while we were there, without our asking!I felt safe and comfortable and would stay there again. The quality of the hotel and staff was much better than I expected for the price! 
